  "key": "C# major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "Are we gonna unite? Or are we fit to die? Which way do you see it all ending, beginning? Wondering what we're feeling each way, each step, just a different day Recollect your thoughts and unite or just die Cause we're untied, don't feel like we're going the same way There's no need to talk about a depressing life because everything goes Are you gonna unite? Or are we here to die? We can't be living separate lives anymore Is that change not good for you? Is that a little bit of a different perspective to show you You're not on the path that you think you should be So are you gonna unite us? Or are you just putting us out to die? As we untie all our lives Will you unite or are you here to die? Like gratitude shows you a different why We all see differently, different than a view of us And if that other piece doesn't unite, it makes you cry at night You should chew it away, put space between you and that idea If it's not working for you, kill it in the end, don't you? Are you willing to unite? Or are you here to suffocate our lives? Make it so it never existed, the easier why of me There's no need to even talk about it, it's clearly that we see different about us So with that, there's nothing to pout or doubt",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 22.979999542236328,
      "text": "Are we gonna unite? Or are we fit to die?",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 30.639999389648438,
      "text": "Which way do you see it all ending, beginning?",
      "start": 22.979999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 35.97999954223633,
      "text": "Wondering what we're feeling each way, each step, just a different day",
      "start": 30.780000686645508
    },
    {
      "end": 42.720001220703125,
      "text": "Recollect your thoughts and unite or just die",
      "start": 37.119998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 48.939998626708984,
      "text": "Cause we're untied, don't feel like we're going the same way",
      "start": 42.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 57.08000183105469,
      "text": "There's no need to talk about a depressing life because everything goes",
      "start": 49.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 63.540000915527344,
      "text": "Are you gonna unite? Or are we here to die?",
      "start": 57.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 71.23999786376953,
      "text": "We can't be living separate lives anymore",
      "start": 64.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 80.76000213623047,
      "text": "Is that change not good for you? Is that a little bit of a different perspective to show you",
      "start": 71.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 85.13999938964844,
      "text": "You're not on the path that you think you should be",
      "start": 80.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 93.0999984741211,
      "text": "So are you gonna unite us? Or are you just putting us out to die?",
      "start": 85.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 99.5199966430664,
      "text": "As we untie all our lives",
      "start": 93.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 105.68000030517578,
      "text": "Will you unite or are you here to die?",
      "start": 100.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 112.19999694824219,
      "text": "Like gratitude shows you a different why",
      "start": 107.5199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 120.26000213623047,
      "text": "We all see differently, different than a view of us",
      "start": 113.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 127.13999938964844,
      "text": "And if that other piece doesn't unite, it makes you cry at night",
      "start": 121.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 134.89999389648438,
      "text": "You should chew it away, put space between you and that idea",
      "start": 127.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 141.94000244140625,
      "text": "If it's not working for you, kill it in the end, don't you?",
      "start": 135.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 151.32000732421875,
      "text": "Are you willing to unite? Or are you here to suffocate our lives?",
      "start": 143.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 157.8000030517578,
      "text": "Make it so it never existed, the easier why of me",
      "start": 152.47999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 167.17999267578125,
      "text": "There's no need to even talk about it, it's clearly that we see different about us",
      "start": 158.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 172.10000610351562,
      "text": "So with that, there's nothing to pout or doubt",
      "start": 167.17999267578125
    }
  ],
  "unlock": {
    "card": "card-65",
    "fragments": 10
  }
}